or ask or anything?

00:24:35.040 --> 00:24:37.270
We do have McNally
Jackson in the back

00:24:37.270 --> 00:24:39.920
with us-- yay-- to have
copies of both "Frog

00:24:39.920 --> 00:24:41.260
Music" and "Room."

00:24:41.260 --> 00:24:42.692
These are the
subsidized editions

00:24:42.692 --> 00:24:45.290
that you can get for $10 cash.

00:24:45.290 --> 00:24:48.699
And maybe Emma will sit
for a few more minutes

00:24:48.699 --> 00:24:49.990
and sign copies of them for us.

00:24:49.990 --> 00:24:51.540
EMMA DONOGHUE: Sure.

00:24:51.540 --> 00:24:53.605
AUDIENCE: So, if anybody
else-- Unless there's

00:24:53.605 --> 00:24:55.244
anything else to
ask, let's just hang

00:24:55.244 --> 00:24:56.660
out and chat for
a couple minutes.

00:24:56.660 --> 00:24:57.260
Thank you Emma.

00:24:57.260 --> 00:24:58.301
EMMA DONOGHUE: Thank you.

00:24:58.301 --> 00:24:59.710
That was fun.

